ğŸ“˜ SECTION 5 â€” Backend API Endpoint Definitions

Since your backend will remain in PHP but become API-based, we define endpoints.


---

5.1 Authentication Endpoints

POST /api/auth/register
POST /api/auth/login
POST /api/auth/verify-passcode (for admins)
POST /api/auth/logout
GET  /api/auth/me


---

5.2 User Management

GET    /api/users
GET    /api/users/{id}
POST   /api/users
PUT    /api/users/{id}
DELETE /api/users/{id}


---

5.3 Exam System

GET    /api/exams
GET    /api/exams/{id}
POST   /api/exams
PUT    /api/exams/{id}
DELETE /api/exams/{id}

POST   /api/exams/{id}/questions
GET    /api/exams/{id}/questions
DELETE /api/questions/{id}

POST   /api/exams/{id}/submit
GET    /api/exams/results/{id}


---

5.4 Payments

POST  /api/payments/upload
GET   /api/payments
GET   /api/payments/{id}
POST  /api/payments/{id}/approve
POST  /api/payments/{id}/reject


---

5.5 Gallery

GET   /api/gallery
POST  /api/gallery
DELETE /api/gallery/{id}


---

5.6 Blog

GET    /api/blog
GET    /api/blog/{id}
POST   /api/blog
PUT    /api/blog/{id}
DELETE /api/blog/{id}


---

ğŸ“˜ SECTION 6 â€” Database Schema Reconstruction
This schema is structured for:

Clean migrations

Easy PHP API consumption

Simple ORM mapping (future Laravel upgrade)

Clear React data handling

Full compliance with your permission roles



---

â­ 6.1 USERS TABLE

Table: users

Field	Type	Description

id	INT (PK, AI)	Unique user ID
full_name	VARCHAR(255)	Full name of ambassador/admin
email	VARCHAR(255)	Unique email
phone	VARCHAR(15)	Phone number
church	VARCHAR(255)	Church name
association	VARCHAR(255)	Association name (from 25 associations list)
role	ENUM('ambassador','president','superadmin')	Defines permission level
age	INT	Age
rank	VARCHAR(50)	Rank (page, squire, knight, etc.)
user_code	VARCHAR(50)	System-generated RA ID
password_hash	VARCHAR(255)	Hashed password
created_at	DATETIME	Timestamp
updated_at	DATETIME	Timestamp
status	ENUM('active','inactive','suspended')	User status
admin_passcode_used	BOOLEAN	True if president/superadmin passcode was used



---

â­ 6.2 ASSOCIATIONS TABLE

Table: associations

Field	Type	Description

id	INT (PK)	Unique ID
name	VARCHAR(255)	Association name (1â€“25)
president_user_id	INT	FK â†’ users(id)
created_at	DATETIME	Timestamp



---

â­ 6.3 EXAMS TABLE

Table: exams

Field	Type	Description

id	INT (PK)	Exam ID
title	VARCHAR(255)	Exam name
description	TEXT	Description
rank_required	VARCHAR(50)	Rank required to access this exam
duration_minutes	INT	Time limit
pass_score	INT	Minimum to pass
created_by	INT	FK â†’ users(id) (super admin)
created_at	DATETIME	Timestamp
updated_at	DATETIME	Timestamp



---

â­ 6.4 QUESTIONS TABLE

Table: questions

Field	Type	Description

id	INT (PK)	Question ID
exam_id	INT	FK â†’ exams(id)
question_text	TEXT	The question
option_a	TEXT	Option A
option_b	TEXT	Option B
option_c	TEXT	Option C
option_d	TEXT	Option D
correct_option	CHAR(1)	A/B/C/D
created_at	DATETIME	Timestamp


Index: exam_id for fast lookup.


---

â­ 6.5 EXAM APPROVAL TABLE

Table: exam_approvals

Field	Type	Description

id	INT (PK)	Approval ID
user_id	INT	Ambassador ID
exam_id	INT	Exam ID
approved_by	INT	President or Super Admin ID
approved_at	DATETIME	Timestamp
status	ENUM('approved','revoked')	Current state



---

â­ 6.6 EXAM SUBMISSIONS TABLE

Table: exam_submissions

Field	Type	Description

id	INT (PK)	Submission ID
user_id	INT	Ambassador ID
exam_id	INT	Exam ID
submitted_at	DATETIME	Time of completion
score	INT	Auto-scored score
passed	BOOLEAN	True if score â‰¥ pass_score
promoted	BOOLEAN	True if user rank changed
promoted_from	VARCHAR(50)	Previous rank
promoted_to	VARCHAR(50)	New rank



---

â­ 6.7 PAYMENTS TABLE

Table: payments

Field	Type	Description

id	INT (PK)	Payment ID
user_id	INT	Ambassador/Admin who paid
association	VARCHAR(255)	Association name
type	ENUM('dues','exam','camp')	Payment type
amount	DECIMAL(10,2)	Amount
receipt_image	VARCHAR(255)	Uploaded receipt path
status	ENUM('pending','approved','rejected')	Approval state
approved_by	INT	Super Admin ID
approved_at	DATETIME	Timestamp
created_at	DATETIME	Upload timestamp



---

â­ 6.8 CAMP REGISTRATIONS TABLE

Table: camp_registrations

Field	Type	Description

id	INT (PK)	Registration ID
user_id	INT	Ambassador
association	VARCHAR(255)	Registrarâ€™s association
year	YEAR	Camp year
status	ENUM('registered','confirmed')	Status
uploaded_by	INT	President/Admin
excel_reference	VARCHAR(255)	Excel file identifier
created_at	DATETIME	Timestamp



---

â­ 6.9 NOTIFICATIONS TABLE

Table: notifications

Field	Type	Description

id	INT (PK)	Notification ID
title	VARCHAR(255)	Title
message	TEXT	Body
target_role	ENUM('ambassador','president','superadmin','all')	Recipients
created_by	INT	User ID
created_at	DATETIME	Timestamp



---

â­ 6.10 BLOG TABLE

Table: blog_posts

Field	Type	Description

id	INT (PK)	Post ID
title	VARCHAR(255)	Title
content	TEXT	Body content
featured_image	VARCHAR(255)	Image
created_by	INT	Super Admin
created_at	DATETIME	Timestamp
updated_at	DATETIME	Timestamp



---

â­ 6.11 GALLERY TABLE

Table: gallery_items

Field	Type	Description

id	INT (PK)	Image ID
image	VARCHAR(255)	Image URL/path
caption	VARCHAR(255)	Optional caption
uploaded_by	INT	Super Admin
created_at	DATETIME	Timestamp



---

â­ 6.12 LOGS TABLE (System Activity)

Table: system_logs

Field	Type	Description

id	INT (PK)	Log ID
user_id	INT	Actor
action	VARCHAR(255)	What happened
ip	VARCHAR(50)	IP Address
created_at	DATETIME	Timestamp

