ğŸ“˜ SECTION 9 â€” Background Animation Specification (A + D)

YOU SELECTED: A + D
(Soft Floating Particles + Gold Glow Pulsing)

These are the exact rules.


---

9.1 Animation Type A â€” Floating Particles

Design

Navy-gold glowing dots

Low density

Slow movement

Slight random drift

Opacity: 0.25â€“0.45

Size: 2pxâ€“5px


Behavior

Particles float slowly downward/upward

Continuous loop

No jitter

Never overlap text or distract


Implementation

Canvas or SVG layer

Positioned behind all content

Tailwind class: absolute inset-0 -z-10



---

9.2 Animation Type D â€” Gold Glow Pulsing

Design

Very subtle gold glow

Pulse intensity: 0â€“0.15 opacity

Radius: around card edges


Behavior

Slow pulse (4â€“6 seconds per cycle)

When hovered â†’ slightly stronger glow


Implementation

Tailwind animations + CSS keyframes

Example keyframe:


@keyframes goldPulse {
  0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(212,175,55,0.1); }
  50% { box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(212,175,55,0.25); }
}


---

